La Strada pizza is one of the hidden pizza jems of brooklyn. Serving the community in and around Maimonides Hospital for as long as I can remember. You not only get one of the best Brooklyn slices of pizza, but really good hot food as well. The crust is not to thick or to thin, it's just right, and always served hot and fresh. If your in the area, and want a good slice, or just some good food, stop in, you will not regret it.
